      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk or anything. just like a single glass of wine with my meal. it's not like i'm going out to a bar. won't a tiny bit of it just make the sleeping pill work more efficiently so i don't toss and turn all night? it seems like it wouldn't be a big deal if the amount is small.",
